  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>The Repairs by Technician and Item Report provides a more detailed look at a technician's work, showing the number of repairs done for each catalog item with cost and profit data. This report pulls data based on the\u00a0<strong>Relations</strong> column when adding an item to a repair ticket.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/image-20230627-153450.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"Reports:RepairsbyTechnicianandItem-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933803762/Reports+Repairs+by+Technician\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933803762\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Repairs by Technician</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933377814/Reports+Repairs+by+Device\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933377814\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Reports: Repairs by Device</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/image-20230627-153447.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Reports:RepairsbyTechnicianandItem-ViewingtheRepairsbyTechnician&amp;ItemReport\">Viewing the Repairs by Technician &amp; Item Report</h2><p>On the Navigation Bar, click\u00a0<strong>Reports</strong>. On the Reports page, click on the <strong>Productivity\u00a0dropdown\u00a0</strong>along the top row of report categories. From the available list, click\u00a0<strong>Repairs by Tech &amp; Item</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/image-20230627-153453.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"411\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/image-20230627-153457.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Use the available filters to scope results based on the assigned parameters.\u00a0Once you have set your filters, click\u00a0<strong>Apply\u00a0Filters\u00a0</strong>to run the report.</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: We recommend viewing productivity based on closed tickets. Once a ticket has been closed, the date will no longer change, and the ticket has been paid in full. This also aligns with our\u00a0<a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1934360642/RepairQ+Accounting+Principles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1934360642\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">accounting principles</a>, as open tickets are considered a liability until the ticket is closed.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/image-20230627-153459.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><strong>Date Range </strong>- Select a date range for your scope of results.</p></li><li><p><strong>Location </strong>- Select a specific location or an aggregate report of all locations.</p></li><li><p><strong>Ticket Status </strong>- Select a specific ticket status or all ticket statuses for your results. The results will reflect the date when the ticket was updated. By default, the report will run for tickets in <strong>Closed</strong> status because this is the most reliable method for this business model.</p></li><li><p><strong>Action</strong> - Filter results by any assigned Ticket Action(s).</p></li><li><p><strong>Resolution</strong> - Filter results by any assigned Ticket Resolution(s).</p></li><li><p><strong>Item Type</strong> - Select a specific item type or all item types.</p></li><li><p><strong>Catalog</strong>\u00a0<strong>Item</strong>\u00a0- Keyword search for a specific catalog item.</p></li><li><p><strong>Include Labor in Total Cost</strong>\u00a0- Labor is added based on hours entered on ticket items and the assigned staff member's pay rate assigned in their profile.</p></li></ul><hr/><h2 id=\"Reports:RepairsbyTechnicianandItem-RepairsbyTechnician&amp;Item\">Repairs by Technician &amp; Item</h2><p>The Repairs by Tech and Item Report provides a combined, detailed look at a technician's work, showing the number of repairs done for each Catalog Item with Cost and Profit data.</p><p>The Profit Margin is calculated by the following equation: Gross Sale - Discounts - Total Cost = Profit Margin.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/Tech%20&amp;%20Item%206.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>(Optional) Click\u00a0<strong>Hide/Show Filters\u00a0</strong>on the upper-right side of the page to collapse/expand the filters when viewing reports.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"253\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/image-20230627-153504.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>Click\u00a0<strong>To Excel\u00a0</strong>on the upper-right side of the report page to export an Excel-friendly document. The export will include any filtered data when running the report.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"253\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1939570735/image-20230627-153507.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
